{{Weapon}}

== Overview ==
Shield Disruptors fire waves of energy which neutralize shields. In combination with [[:Category:Weapons (Light Armor Piercing)|armor piercing weapons]] such as Auto Cannons, [[:Category:Weapons (Shield Disruptors)|Shield Disruptors]] can prove quite effective.

== Where to Acquire ==
The Shield Disruptor can be bought in the workshop or found in caves, vaults, and bot remains in Vulcore.
